'''maundy'''
# {{obsolete}} A [[commandment]].
# {{obsolete}} The [[sacrament]] of the [[Lord]]'s [[supper]].
# The ceremony of [[wash]]ing the [[foot|feet]] of [[poor]] persons or [[inferior]]s, performed as a [[religious]] [[rite]] on [[Maundy Thursday]] in commemoration of [[Christ]]'s washing the [[disciple]]s' feet at the [[last supper]].
# The [[office]] appointed to be read during the ceremony of [[feet-washing]].

